  encounterName: 
  text: The shimmering light of this island intrigues you. Getting closer, the air
    around it is warped and faintly glowing. A quiet hum comes from deep within the
    island, slowly turning into a voice. "Our treasure has been stolen. If you return
    it to us, we can finally rest...".
